    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/df6f1737794d85178fbb90fc96c1fa6b.poster.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/df6f1737794d85178fbb90fc96c1fa6b.webm?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>炼金术师朱斯来到驯鹿河对付当地游荡的邪魔。你将化身只属于你的朱斯，探索现已变成荒野的新英格兰，通过动作角色扮演游戏经典的等距俯视角或者子弹时间形式的近战对抗恶魔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/c0c2ae9fc547407b1862b093bb07dbf3.poster.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/c0c2ae9fc547407b1862b093bb07dbf3.webm?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/c0c2ae9fc547407b1862b093bb07dbf3.mp4?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>寻找、制作改变一切的重要物品，根据自己的游戏习惯配制药剂，娴熟驾驭《阳间大炼金术师》的牌组构建机制。除了角色自定义以外，运用仪式魔法创造长效增益，赋予角色与众不同的特点。面对交叉路口的奇怪生物，见证黑暗剧情的发展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/9488f7aaf4c1830c9615f52a365f91ed.poster.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/9488f7aaf4c1830c9615f52a365f91ed.webm?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/9488f7aaf4c1830c9615f52a365f91ed.mp4?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/aec40006d9ec4da14c636545b507eab9.webp?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=27 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的物品与角色流派</h2><br><i>获取战利品，制作物品</i><br>作为一名炼金术士，你不穿盔甲，不挥舞宝剑，却能向敌人倾泻火焰。在荒野中寻找具有独特属性的烧瓶，或在工作台上制作它们。以卡组建造的方式创建一个烧瓶汇编，并从中随机抽取。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/34287fe22d240c5b403c225f8677aed4.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=182 /></span><br><br><i>技能系统独树一帜</i><br>在《阳间大炼金术师》，烧瓶就是技能。每瓶药剂不仅可以正常使用，有时还会得到强化，产生更强的效果。部分烧瓶本身具有特质，可以显著改变药剂的使用效果，便于你开发属于自己的玩法风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/aec40006d9ec4da14c636545b507eab9.webp?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=27 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索黑暗世界</h2><br><i>地形程序生成，城镇人工绘制</i><br>《阳间大炼金术师》的世界分为若干广阔的关卡，地形均为程序生成。所有峡谷、大海、江河、山峦、建筑、石头、树木和物品均由特殊算法生成，即便完成了主线剧情，依然可以继续探索。不过，任务地点还是人工打造，以便讲述扣人心弦的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/ac1927f758307eb6600f9964853e4821.poster.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/ac1927f758307eb6600f9964853e4821.webm?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/ac1927f758307eb6600f9964853e4821.mp4?t=1751306569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>黑暗之地等你发现</i><br>你和敌人都会受日夜循环和天气效果影响。不过，邪魔不断出现，敌人还会因此而获得增强。找到黑暗祭坛，遏止邪魔的影响，发现更多秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/aec40006d9ec4da14c636545b507eab9.webp?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=27 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗引人入胜</h2><br><i>动作角色扮演游戏经典等距视角</i><br>经典俯视角远程攻击敌人，投掷爆炸药水或者冰冻药剂，利用炸药桶埋伏敌人。“蛙跳”烧瓶能让你跳出险境或者切至近身战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384060/extras/278916d73672a9a52ccd89aa17ee49de.avif?t=1751306569\" width=616 height=182 /></span><br><br><i>子弹时间形式的近身战斗</i><br>进入近身战斗状态，闪躲或者借助烟雾烧瓶躲避攻击，直接与敌人互动。交叉路口的敌人可怖骇人，一对一战斗激烈刺激，期间务必合理使用资源和药剂。<br><br>",
